---
// Faixa de destaque na home que leva pra LP do Plano Ton Black.
---
<section class="relative bg-ink-950 text-paper overflow-hidden">
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 -right-20 -translate-y-1/2 w-[560px] h-[560px] rounded-full bg-ton/12 blur-[110px]"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative container-x py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-center">
      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-ton/30 bg-ton/10 px-3 py-1 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] font-mono text-ton">
          <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-ton animate-pulse"></span>
          Exclusivo MEI e CNPJ
        </span>

        <h2 class="mt-5 text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-paper leading-[1.1]">
          Fatura acima de R$ 20 mil por mês?
          <span class="block mt-2 text-ton">Você tem direito ao Plano Ton Black.</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="mt-5 text-sm md:text-base text-ink-200/85 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
          Débito a partir de <strong class="text-paper">0,74%</strong>, crédito à vista a partir de
          <strong class="text-paper">2,68%</strong> e Pix sempre 0%. Quanto maior o seu volume, menor a taxa.
          A gente faz a análise gratuita da sua taxa atual e mostra em números quanto você economiza por mês.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
          <a href="/ton-black" class="btn btn-wa" data-cta="home-black-cta">
            Conhecer o Ton Black
            <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-ink-700 bg-ink-900/60 p-5">
            <div class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-ton">Débito</div>
            <div class="mt-2 font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-paper leading-none">0,74%</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-[11px] text-ink-300">a partir de</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-ink-700 bg-ink-900/60 p-5">
            <div class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-ton">Crédito à vista</div>
            <div class="mt-2 font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-paper leading-none">2,68%</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-[11px] text-ink-300">a partir de</div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-span-2 rounded-2xl border border-ton/40 bg-ton/10 p-5">
            <div class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-ton">Pix</div>
            <div class="mt-2 font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-ton leading-none">0% ilimitado</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-[11px] text-ink-200/80">sem taxa, sem limite, cai na hora</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
